1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
♪Because you exist♪

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
♪You're always♪

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
♪Hold tight♪

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,145
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 24=

9
00:00:53,579 --> 00:00:54,739
This auction's

10
00:00:54,740 --> 00:00:56,298
success

11
00:00:56,299 --> 00:00:58,019
is largely thanks to Ms. Mu.

12
00:00:58,059 --> 00:01:00,819
As for me, I've always been a layman
when it comes to auctions.

13
00:01:00,820 --> 00:01:02,049
From now on,

14
00:01:02,050 --> 00:01:04,299
(Moser International)

15
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:06,340
I'll leave the company
entirely in your hands, Ms. Mu.

16
00:01:11,562 --> 00:01:15,920
(Moser International)

17
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:26,659
Mr. Shen, when did you start
moonlighting as a masseur?

18
00:01:29,059 --> 00:01:30,498
So, how is my technique,

19
00:01:30,499 --> 00:01:31,299
Ms. Mu?

20
00:01:34,699 --> 00:01:35,980
It's just so-so.

21
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:41,179
Ms. Mu,

22
00:01:42,339 --> 00:01:44,140
do you remember what you promised me?

23
00:01:45,339 --> 00:01:46,498
I'm not sure

24
00:01:46,499 --> 00:01:48,379
which matter
you're referring to, Mr. Shen.

25
00:01:49,859 --> 00:01:51,099
Find some time

26
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,620
to get married.

27
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,620
What if I back out?

28
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,340
Back out?

29
00:02:00,339 --> 00:02:01,659
Then I will

30
00:02:03,419 --> 00:02:05,060
tie you up and take you away.

31
00:02:08,059 --> 00:02:10,139
Zhiyu! Boss is coming to pick you up soon.

32
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:12,180
How big a red envelope
should I ask him for?

33
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:14,620
Ask for a lot.

34
00:02:14,819 --> 00:02:16,378
Take a hit on his wallet.

35
00:02:16,379 --> 00:02:18,819
Zhiyu, I knew you loved me the most!

36
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:27,740
What are you doing here?

37
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:28,620
Move.

38
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:31,400
I haven't settled the score with you
for tricking me last time.

39
00:02:32,059 --> 00:02:33,220
Why are you here?

40
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:34,659
Yu.

41
00:02:37,619 --> 00:02:38,939
You look truly beautiful today.

42
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:43,020
You are not welcome here.

43
00:02:43,059 --> 00:02:44,139
Please leave.

44
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:45,500
Yu,

45
00:02:45,779 --> 00:02:46,658
don't you want to know

46
00:02:46,659 --> 00:02:48,859
the real cause of your adoptive father
Mu Chenzhou's death?

47
00:02:50,659 --> 00:02:51,378
Zhiyu,

48
00:02:51,379 --> 00:02:52,459
don't listen to his nonsense.

49
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:54,139
Today is the big day for you and Boss.

50
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:55,460
He's just here to sabotage it.

51
00:02:55,659 --> 00:02:57,020
(The cause of my dad's death?)

52
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,340
I'll go with you.

53
00:03:15,939 --> 00:03:17,220
We meet again,

54
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,659
Miss Mu.

55
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:28,659
You two are actually
in league with each other.

56
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,818
Well, we both have a grudge

57
00:03:31,819 --> 00:03:33,099
against Shen Jibai.

58
00:04:45,219 --> 00:04:46,380
Boss Shen,

59
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:49,220
it's time we settled our account.

60
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:51,900
Shen Jibai!

61
00:04:52,219 --> 00:04:53,220
Don't move.

62
00:04:54,099 --> 00:04:56,019
You'd better do exactly as I say.

63
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,939
Xu Mingzhu, I'm warning you,
don't do anything reckless.

64
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:58,979
Xu Mingzhu,

65
00:04:59,419 --> 00:05:00,659
what do you mean by this?

66
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,680
Didn't we agree to only use her
to threaten Shen Jibai

67
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,578
and not to touch her?

68
00:05:03,580 --> 00:05:05,538
Take one more step,
and I won't be polite.

69
00:05:05,539 --> 00:05:06,738
Don't you dare touch her!

70
00:05:06,739 --> 00:05:07,659
Stay back.

71
00:05:08,299 --> 00:05:09,978
Do you think Mu Zhiyu

72
00:05:09,979 --> 00:05:12,059
will treat you any better
if you do this?

73
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:14,218
I'll give you
however much money you want.

74
00:05:14,219 --> 00:05:15,140
Let her go.

75
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:19,020
He Group can barely
save itself right now.

76
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,299
How much money could you possibly have?

77
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,699
I should have known
you were this kind of person.

78
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,979
You are burning bridges.
I should never have trusted you.

79
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:28,899
Xu Mingzhu,

80
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,739
a person like you
who does nothing but evil,

81
00:05:30,779 --> 00:05:32,140
will not come to a good end.

82
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:34,299
Well, haven't you heard

83
00:05:34,339 --> 00:05:37,538
that the good die young, while the wicked
live for a thousand years?

84
00:05:37,539 --> 00:05:39,240
Shen Jibai won't let you
get away with this.

85
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,418
You're still thinking
about Shen Jibai coming to save you?

86
00:05:41,419 --> 00:05:43,299
I was the one who killed his parents.

87
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,900
You killed Ye Li too?

88
00:05:46,219 --> 00:05:47,179
That's right.

89
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:49,099
It's not too late to find out now.

90
00:05:49,299 --> 00:05:50,979
At least you can die knowing the truth.

91
00:05:52,179 --> 00:05:53,580
This face of yours

92
00:05:53,859 --> 00:05:56,632
is so beautiful
that it's absolutely annoying.

93
00:05:57,979 --> 00:05:59,659
- I'll slash your face first.
- Zhiyu!

94
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:00,820
No!

95
00:06:01,179 --> 00:06:02,099
Don't come any closer.

96
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,580
Xu Mingzhu,

97
00:06:04,779 --> 00:06:05,859
let Zhiyu go.

98
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,700
I'll give you whatever you want.

99
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:10,739
If you want to save her,

100
00:06:12,260 --> 00:06:13,619
stab yourself.

101
00:06:14,179 --> 00:06:15,380
Don't listen to her.

102
00:06:16,099 --> 00:06:18,218
I'll give you as much money as you want,
just let him go.

103
00:06:18,219 --> 00:06:19,419
Shut up!

104
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:21,140
Boss Shen.

105
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:22,940
I want to see

106
00:06:23,859 --> 00:06:25,380
if you actually have any guts.

107
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,419
No.

108
00:06:31,779 --> 00:06:33,220
No, Shen Jibai.

109
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,659
No.

110
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,619
No!

111
00:07:18,779 --> 00:07:21,858
I didn't expect Mu Chenzhou to
raise such a sentimental fool like you.

112
00:07:21,859 --> 00:07:23,260
It's quite a surprise.

113
00:07:24,339 --> 00:07:26,299
I know you're in good shape,

114
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:27,619
but

115
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:30,380
if you don't stop the bleeding in time,

116
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:32,059
I'm afraid you won't make it.

117
00:07:33,299 --> 00:07:34,140
How about this?

118
00:07:34,299 --> 00:07:35,780
Let's make this quick.

119
00:07:35,979 --> 00:07:37,699
Tell me the code to the safe,

120
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,080
and I'll let you both go immediately.

121
00:07:39,979 --> 00:07:41,460
I really don't know the code.

122
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,619
But if it's money you want,

123
00:07:44,219 --> 00:07:45,379
I'll give you any amount.

124
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:46,580
Don't lie to me!

125
00:07:47,016 --> 00:07:48,774
You're the sole heir to Mu Group.

126
00:07:48,775 --> 00:07:50,256
How could you not know?

127
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:51,419
I'm telling you,

128
00:07:51,739 --> 00:07:54,020
I want both the money and the code.

129
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,820
Xu Mingzhu,

130
00:08:00,099 --> 00:08:02,580
there's no need for us
to lie to you at this point.

131
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:04,099
If you keep dragging this out,

132
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,859
all you're going to get

133
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,700
are Shen Jibai's and my lives.

134
00:08:07,779 --> 00:08:09,499
Don't threaten me.

135
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:13,539
Ms. Xu.

136
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:16,936
- Protect the Boss.
- Shen Jibai!

137
00:08:16,937 --> 00:08:20,759
♪Ten years of the past
have turned to smoke♪

138
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:24,338
♪I close my innocent eyes♪

139
00:08:24,339 --> 00:08:24,761
Go.

140
00:08:24,762 --> 00:08:26,499
♪No more parting by life or death♪

141
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,619
- Take them.
- Let go of me!

142
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:28,739
Shen Jibai,

143
00:08:29,179 --> 00:08:30,098
don't fall asleep.

144
00:08:30,099 --> 00:08:31,700
Don't...

145
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:34,979
Don't fall asleep, Shen Jibai.

146
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,300
I'm okay.

147
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:43,899
I thought you...

148
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:46,982
♪From now on, no one can break it♪

149
00:08:47,779 --> 00:08:49,060
Don't cry.

150
00:08:49,819 --> 00:08:51,099
I'm fine.

151
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:56,460
Why were you so foolish?

152
00:08:57,179 --> 00:08:59,460
You stabbed yourself
just because they told you to.

153
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,979
If you had just now...

154
00:09:05,939 --> 00:09:07,340
I promised you

155
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:10,859
that I would protect you
for the rest of my life.

156
00:09:10,912 --> 00:09:13,658
♪The green flower breaks in two♪

157
00:09:13,659 --> 00:09:15,061
It's just a minor injury.

158
00:09:15,062 --> 00:09:19,259
♪Our hearts will be together at last♪

159
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:19,986
It's fine.

160
00:09:19,987 --> 00:09:23,924
♪Waking up between our dreams♪

161
00:09:23,925 --> 00:09:27,961
♪Drawing a circle of falling blossoms
to record your book of poetry♪

162
00:09:27,962 --> 00:09:32,074
♪If destined souls must part,
the broken mirror shall mend again♪

163
00:09:32,075 --> 00:09:36,807
♪In this life, one life given
in exchange for a lifelong bond♪

164
00:09:36,887 --> 00:09:41,657
♪And a promise of safety for a lifetime♪

165
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:52,540
The code to the safe...

166
00:10:23,662 --> 00:10:26,149
♪The fragmented, peaceful♪

167
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:28,349
♪Tiniest dream♪

168
00:10:28,350 --> 00:10:29,698
♪Slips through the window by chance♪

169
00:10:29,699 --> 00:10:30,739
For the rest of my life,

170
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:33,058
♪Shines into my life♪

171
00:10:33,059 --> 00:10:34,940
I will use my life

172
00:10:35,179 --> 00:10:36,574
to keep you safe.

173
00:10:36,575 --> 00:10:39,670
♪That light is you♪

174
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:43,161
♪Because you appeared♪

175
00:10:43,162 --> 00:10:45,211
♪My world becomes hazy♪

176
00:10:45,212 --> 00:10:47,299
♪Advancing while retreating♪

177
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:49,361
♪Guessing how you feel♪

178
00:10:49,362 --> 00:10:51,399
♪You'll never understand♪

179
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,549
♪These random emotions♪

180
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:56,111
♪Are controlled by you♪

181
00:10:56,112 --> 00:10:57,999
♪I want to ask♪

182
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:01,824
♪Will you care about
my feelings once more?♪

183
00:11:01,825 --> 00:11:06,520
♪Will you let me walk
into your heart in the deep of night?♪

184
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:09,720
♪Not daring to think too much♪

185
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:11,099
(Shen Jibai,)

186
00:11:11,579 --> 00:11:12,660
(this time,)

187
00:11:13,179 --> 00:11:14,899
(I believe you unconditionally.)

188
00:11:15,459 --> 00:11:16,739
(From now on,)

189
00:11:17,179 --> 00:11:19,019
(there will be no evasion or doubt)

190
00:11:19,459 --> 00:11:20,619
(between us.)

191
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,739
(We will hold each other's hands.)

192
00:11:22,779 --> 00:11:25,000
(Just like this,
we will keep walking forward together.)

193
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,538
(The 8th China Auctioneer)
The winner of this year's Golden Hammer Award

194
00:11:27,539 --> 00:11:28,979
(Golden Hammer Awards)
is Miss Mu Zhiyu.

195
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:31,060
Let's give her a round of applause.

196
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,700
(Police found the remains
of Mu Chenzhou in an abandoned factory.)

197
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:54,900
(Forensics confirmed Mu Chenzhou died of
multi-organ failure)

198
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:56,440
(caused by long-term sedative injections
by Zhao Ye under Xu Mingzhu's orders.)

199
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,760
(Xu Mingzhu created the illusion that
Ye Li "died of depression" to cover up her murder.)

200
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:58,719
(Xu Mingzhu was sentenced to death
with a 2-year reprieve.)

201
00:11:58,719 --> 00:11:59,880
(He Min was sentenced to five years in prison.)

202
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,560
(Zhao Ye was sentenced to nine years.
Scarface Jiang Hu was sentenced to twelve years.)

203
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:05,880
(The End)

204
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,880
(Thank you for your company)

205
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,280
(May you find your own love and care in life)

206
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,040
(and be tightly surrounded
by tenderness and warmth.)

207
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:17,959
♪Will you let me walk
into your heart in the deep of night?♪

208
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:21,039
♪Not daring to think too much♪

209
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:26,319
♪To see if you like me♪

210
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:30,349
♪Will you occasionally
wait for me by your phone?♪

211
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:34,599
♪Will the music you share be about me?♪

212
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:38,119
♪Not daring to say too much♪

213
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:46,120
♪Perhaps you already
understand my heart♪

214
00:13:01,812 --> 00:13:06,361
♪Will there be a day
when your eyes are full of me?♪

215
00:13:06,362 --> 00:13:10,840
♪Will you think of calling me first
when you pick up your phone?♪

216
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:13,879
♪My rainbow starry sky♪

217
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:18,759
♪Is painted entirely with your smile♪

218
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:22,959
♪If you could stop dodging me♪

219
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:27,599
♪If I am becoming
a better version of myself for you♪

220
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:30,799
♪No need to say too much♪

221
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:39,600
♪I think I already understand your heart♪
